HEADWORD: forward-looking
<hw>forward-looking</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>planning for the future;
concerned primarily with the future; -- contrasted with conern for the
immediate present or reacting to past events.</def>
<contr>backward-looking</contr>⟦br⟧
